OL,3,CPolice offer 'empty apology' to
OL,4,CHillsborough parents
OL,6,FJenni Hicks spoke to ITV following the
OL,7,Fapology
OL,9,FThe parents of teenage sisters killed
OL,10,Fin the Hillsborough disaster say a new
OL,11,Fapology from the police means nothing
OL,12,Fwithout further action.
OL,14,FJenni and Trevor Hicks want to correct
OL,15,Fofficial court records, which wrongly
OL,16,Fstate their daughters Victoria and
OL,17,FSarah lost consciousness within 30
OL,18,Fseconds and died a short time later,
OL,19,Fwhen in fact they suffered much longer.
