OL,6,FThe record cannot be officially
OL,7,Fcorrected without the consent of South
OL,8,FYorkshire Police (SYP), which Jenni
OL,9,Fand her former husband Trevor Hicks
OL,10,Fsay they have not received so far.
OL,12,FThe Chief Constable of SYP, Lauren
OL,13,FPoultney, has said the force "will
OL,14,Ftake the steps available to us to
OL,15,Fsupport the families".
