OL,6,FThis has infuriated the parents and
OL,7,Ftheir legal team, who say there is a
OL,8,F"simple and straightforward" way for
OL,9,FSYP to fix the records by agreeing to
OL,10,Ftestify in open court ` which it has
OL,11,Fnot done.
OL,13,FA new apology was read out in the
OL,14,FHouse of Lords on the evening of
OL,15,FMonday 9 February, but Jenni Hicks
OL,16,Fsaid: "It's nice to have those words
OL,17,Fbut we need it following up with
OL,18,Factions.
