OL,3,CPolice offer 'empty apology' to
OL,4,CHillsborough parents
OL,6,F"They have to prove how sorry they are
OL,7,Fby giving this statement in open court
OL,8,Fotherwise it is just an empty apology."
OL,10,FNinety-seven Liverpool supporters were
OL,11,Funlawfully killed at the FA Cup semi-
OL,12,Ffinal on 15 April 1989, after police
OL,13,Fopened an exit gate to relieve
OL,14,Fcrowding outside the stadium and
OL,15,Ffailed to divert fans away from the
OL,16,Ftunnel leading to the central pens,
OL,17,Fwhere the fatal crush occurred.
