OL,3,CPolice offer 'empty apology' to
OL,4,CHillsborough parents
OL,6,FThey are now calling for the
OL,7,Fintroduction of a "Hicks Rule", to
OL,8,Fmake it easier for people in similar
OL,9,Fcircumstances to correct the official
OL,10,Flegal record.
OL,12,FJenni and Trevor Hicks attended a
OL,13,Fparliamentary event on Monday 9
OL,14,FFebruary alongside legal experts,
OL,15,Fpeers, and MPs, to review the
OL,16,Fsituation.
OL,18,FJenni Hicks said: "For more than three
OL,19,Fdecades, the law has recorded
OL,20,Fsomething about our daughters that we
OL,21,Fnow know simply isn't true.
